extends layout/index
block content
  header.page-section
    .container
      h2.page-section-title Our sponsoring partners
      p.section-subtitle.center Let's grow together.
  section.page-section.sponsors
    .container.small
      p
        | If you&apos;re interested in becoming a sponsoring partner, we&apos;d 
        a(href='mailto:jnjconference@gmail.com') love to chat
        | . We look forward to working with companies and organizations ready and excited to help further English education and training in Korea.
      h4.sponsor-section-title Our Hosting Partners
      // JJU
      ul.sponsor-list
        li.sponsor-list-item.hosting-partner
          a(href='http://www.jj.ac.kr/')
            img.sponsor-logo(src='/img/sponsors/jju-logo.png')
        li.sponsor-list-item.hosting-partner
          h5.sponsor-name Jeonju University
          p.sponsor-description
            | Jeonju University is a private university located on the west end of Jeonju. It has been host to the Jeonju-North Jeolla KOTESOL chapters workshops and Conferences since 2014.
      // KOTESOL
      ul.sponsor-list
        li.sponsor-list-item.hosting-partner
          a(href='https://koreatesol.org/')
            img.sponsor-logo(src='/img/sponsors/kotesol-landscape.png')
        li.sponsor-list-item.hosting-partner
          h5.sponsor-name KOTESOL
          p.sponsor-description
            | KOTESOL is a non-profit, professional organization that seeks to assist teachers in self-development and improve English Language Teaching in Korea.
